  "text": "Comprehensive studies have been carried out to investigate the significance of clock gene perturbations, at the cellular and organismal levels. An extensive RNAi screen in human cells delivered new insights into the effects of clock gene knockdown on circadian rhythms, showing that complex changes within the circadian clock network occur [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
